{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/creative/sketch-jike-plugin/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"45ed7ac5-7c68-5d9e-add1-726884c269e3","excerpt":"…","html":"<p>我们每天被微信这款黑洞应用吸去了大量的时间，想要摆脱它却又怎么也摆脱不掉。关朋友圈、取关公众号、退闲聊群，却仍然解决不了问题。其实想要摆脱这款黑洞应用也很简单，我们只需要再找另一款黑洞应用代替它就可以了。</p>\n<p>最近有一款黄色的应用就很适合作为另一个黑洞。当然我说的黄色是指它的图标是浅黄色的，但这个黄色的图标下却有着丰富的内涵。对于设计师来说，这是一款能够给你带来灵感，激起你无限创意的应用。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 585px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/939de95c14bed9466f502a4aaeab4878/52eca/sketch.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sketch\"\n        title=\"sketch\"\n        src=\"/static/939de95c14bed9466f502a4aaeab4878/52eca/sketch.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/939de95c14bed9466f502a4aaeab4878/0913d/sketch.jpg 160w,\n/static/939de95c14bed9466f502a4aaeab4878/cb69c/sketch.jpg 320w,\n/static/939de95c14bed9466f502a4aaeab4878/52eca/sketch.jpg 585w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>你以为我说的是这个常驻 Dock 栏的黄色大钻石吗？当然不是，我要说的是“每天十分钟，看点好东西”的即刻。即刻会根据你关注的主题，给你推荐各种你想看的信息，比如川普又发推特啦、又有大公司被收购啦等等，让你在工作之余放松一下大脑。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39702c9697f99616ed14fc27eb08cea0/1cfc2/ojbk.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ojbk\"\n        title=\"ojbk\"\n        src=\"/static/39702c9697f99616ed14fc27eb08cea0/6af66/ojbk.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/39702c9697f99616ed14fc27eb08cea0/69538/ojbk.png 160w,\n/static/39702c9697f99616ed14fc27eb08cea0/72799/ojbk.png 320w,\n/static/39702c9697f99616ed14fc27eb08cea0/6af66/ojbk.png 640w,\n/static/39702c9697f99616ed14fc27eb08cea0/1cfc2/ojbk.png 900w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>但是，正如文首提到的，这也是一款黑洞应用，上瘾了每天可不止十分钟。所以你上班总是拿着手机在那刷，被老板看见了也不太好。那有没有一种办法可以一边刷即刻，一边又不被老板看出来呢？</p>\n<p>那就来试试我刚写的这款 Sketch 插件吧！</p>\n<p>你可以在电脑上前往下面的地址下载安装，这个过程我就不多说了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/leadream/jike-sketch-plugin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/leadream/jike-sketch-plugin</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0bc1945eb18d50f7b86157a9232df95c/9d3af/run.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.37499999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"run\"\n        title=\"run\"\n        src=\"/static/0bc1945eb18d50f7b86157a9232df95c/c08c5/run.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0bc1945eb18d50f7b86157a9232df95c/0913d/run.jpg 160w,\n/static/0bc1945eb18d50f7b86157a9232df95c/cb69c/run.jpg 320w,\n/static/0bc1945eb18d50f7b86157a9232df95c/c08c5/run.jpg 640w,\n/static/0bc1945eb18d50f7b86157a9232df95c/9d3af/run.jpg 878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>安装好之后，新建一个 Sketch 空白文档（切记：<strong>不要在你的项目文件里面尝试，不然你的文件可能会被弄乱</strong>），点击顶部菜单栏，依次选择 Plugins -> OJBK -> GO! 就开始运行我们的插件啦。</p>\n<p>此时会弹出一个对话框，让你输入一个即刻主题的链接。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/673e3fa7a4a839c395bcacc1963742ae/7a3d6/input-link.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"input link\"\n        title=\"input link\"\n        src=\"/static/673e3fa7a4a839c395bcacc1963742ae/6af66/input-link.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/673e3fa7a4a839c395bcacc1963742ae/69538/input-link.png 160w,\n/static/673e3fa7a4a839c395bcacc1963742ae/72799/input-link.png 320w,\n/static/673e3fa7a4a839c395bcacc1963742ae/6af66/input-link.png 640w,\n/static/673e3fa7a4a839c395bcacc1963742ae/d9199/input-link.png 960w,\n/static/673e3fa7a4a839c395bcacc1963742ae/7a3d6/input-link.png 990w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>现在里面有一个默认的主题链接，这是一个名叫“微信新动向”的主题，我们直接点击 OK。如果没有意外的话，过一两秒之后你的 Sketch 空文档中间会出现一个新的画板，里面就是这个插件在该主题下抓取的最新的几条动态。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6de2e7e8dcc3eeb6a73b5ace43352ca7/ec5f6/result.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.37499999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"result\"\n        title=\"result\"\n        src=\"/static/6de2e7e8dcc3eeb6a73b5ace43352ca7/6af66/result.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6de2e7e8dcc3eeb6a73b5ace43352ca7/69538/result.png 160w,\n/static/6de2e7e8dcc3eeb6a73b5ace43352ca7/72799/result.png 320w,\n/static/6de2e7e8dcc3eeb6a73b5ace43352ca7/6af66/result.png 640w,\n/static/6de2e7e8dcc3eeb6a73b5ace43352ca7/d9199/result.png 960w,\n/static/6de2e7e8dcc3eeb6a73b5ace43352ca7/21b4d/result.png 1280w,\n/static/6de2e7e8dcc3eeb6a73b5ace43352ca7/ec5f6/result.png 1852w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>为了让你的画板看起来干净利落，我没有把抓取的图片贴上去（其实是不会做），也没有给它添加额外的样式（其实是懒得做）。简直完美，即使老板已经在你身后，你也可以理直气壮地和TA说，“我是一个追求完美的人，所以我要用真实的文本填充设计图”。</p>\n<p>你可能会问，假如我想看其他的主题呢？很简单，去即刻 app 中按下图找到相应主题的链接，再次启动该插件并复制链接到对话框中就可以了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0d1d7fd9f065069d3026dc01362314f7/133ae/get-link.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 88.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"get link\"\n        title=\"get link\"\n        src=\"/static/0d1d7fd9f065069d3026dc01362314f7/6af66/get-link.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0d1d7fd9f065069d3026dc01362314f7/69538/get-link.png 160w,\n/static/0d1d7fd9f065069d3026dc01362314f7/72799/get-link.png 320w,\n/static/0d1d7fd9f065069d3026dc01362314f7/6af66/get-link.png 640w,\n/static/0d1d7fd9f065069d3026dc01362314f7/d9199/get-link.png 960w,\n/static/0d1d7fd9f065069d3026dc01362314f7/21b4d/get-link.png 1280w,\n/static/0d1d7fd9f065069d3026dc01362314f7/133ae/get-link.png 1424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>从今天开始，用 Sketch 愉快地刷即刻吧。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"设计师上班想刷即刻怎么办？","date":"2018/04/04","description":"设计师上班如何刷即刻。","color":"#FFF","cover":"sketch-jike-plugin.jpg","demo":"https://github.com/leadream/jike-sketch-plugin","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/creative/sketch-jike-plugin/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/writing/framer-tutorial/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"《Framer 原型设计指南》在豆瓣阅读专栏上线"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tools/weixin-fullscreen/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"如何获得更加沉浸式的公众号写作体验？"}}}}}